OL,3,CHealth service ombudsman visits town
OL,4,Cafter receiving 100 complaints
OL,6,FAn investigator tasked with looking
OL,7,Finto NHS complaints is in Blackpool -
OL,8,Fafter receiving more than 100
OL,9,Fcomplaints in the town since 2021.
OL,11,F(PHSO) Rob Behrens is hoping to
OL,12,Fencourage others in the resort to flag
OL,13,Fconcerns when things go wrong.
OL,15,FOne case raised with the Ombudsman was
OL,16,Fthat of May Ashord, a mum-of-three
OL,17,Ffrom North Shore, who died from an
OL,18,Foperable brain tumour.
